Privacy Policy for Nirmaan.Market

Effective Date: 28th October 2024

1. Introduction

Nirmaan.Market (“we,” “us,” or “our”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share personal information collected through our website and lead generation forms.

2. Information We Collect

We collect the following personal information from you:

	•	Contact Information: Name, phone number, and email address.
	•	Demographic Information: Information that helps us better understand your interests and needs.
	•	Additional Information: Any other details you provide in forms or during communication with us.

3. How We Use Your Information

The information collected is used to:

	•	Respond to your inquiries and provide information about our products and services.
	•	Process requests for specific services.
	•	Improve our services and provide a better user experience.
	•	Send you updates, promotions, or relevant information about our offerings.

4. Information Sharing

We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share your data with:

	•	Service Providers: We may use third-party service providers to help manage our business operations and provide better service. For example, we may use CRM systems to store your contact information.
	•	Compliance and Legal Requests: We may disclose information where required by law or to comply with legal processes.

5. Data Security

We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no online data transmission is entirely secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

6. Your Rights

Depending on your location, you may have the right to:

	•	Access and receive a copy of your personal information.
	•	Request correction or deletion of your personal information.
	•	Object to the processing of your personal information.

If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact us at [Your Contact Email Address].

7. Updates to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

8. Contact Us

